data.description: New price!! Come check out this spacious two story farmhouse!  If you are looking to have room to spread out, this is your place.  Augusta County location not far from Staunton.  Location, Location, Location!  Riverheads School District! Large bright kitchen, with a huge pantry! Watch the wildlife from your kitchen window. Spacious bedrooms, with master bedroom on the first floor. Fourth bedroom could be a huge office, den, or craftroom.  Parking on both sides of the house.  A gardening space.  Huge shed/barn for the mechanic or farmer with electric. Sit outside on the huge front porch and relax. Come see the possibilities!  The owner is offering a home warranty with an acceptable offer.
data.whatILove: Sitting on either porch watching the deer play in the backyard and fields around us. The quietness is amazing out here and a wonderful place for kids to grow up.
